cs.CL, cs.LG, cs.AI, cs.NE, cs.CV 

This paper is likely to belong to the arXiv CS sub-category of cs.CL (Computation and Language) as it deals with natural language processing (NLP) models and word vector spaces. It could also belong to cs.LG (Machine Learning) as it involves training a neural model. Additionally, it could be categorized under cs.AI (Artificial Intelligence) as it deals with the interpretation of AI models. The paper's focus on non-linear relations between word vectors and concepts suggests it could also be classified under cs.NE (Neural and Evolutionary Computing). Finally, the potential application of the model to computer vision tasks could place it under cs.CV (Computer Vision).
